  {
    "id": "f_csv_d9cb9eac6b",
    "slug": "for-a-scientist-must-indeed-be-freely-imaginative-and-yet-skeptical-creative-an",
    "texto": "For a scientist must indeed be freely imaginative and yet skeptical, creative and yet a critic. There is a sense in which he must be free, but another in which his thought must be very precisely regimented; there is poetry in science, but also a lot of bookkeeping.",
